{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act20side", "eventName": "理想城：長夏狂歡季", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "IC-6", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "戰逃反應", "storyInfo": "來到對岸隧道的眾人發現了意料之外的危機，際崖城隨時可能被活性化的源石礦脈毀滅。眾人爭論不休時，嘉維爾提出可以去地上避難。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "30_i03", "x": 0.0, "y": 0.0, "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$bat_Imfxingback_intro", "key": "$bat_Imfxingback_loop", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 0.87, "yScaleTo": 0.87, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.85, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斯第奇掙扎著睜開眼，看到了兩個熟悉的身影。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿芙朵嘉，我幫你把換洗的衣服帶來了。", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "謝謝。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，克羅綺，我建議你，以後還是少喝點酒比較好。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊哈哈，抱歉抱歉。但是，你看，結果來說不是還挺好嗎？", "name": "克羅綺·磚石"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是看不出有哪裡好了......", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我還是找個地方換衣服吧。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，兩人也注意到了斯第奇的醒來。"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，早上好，斯第奇。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我怎麼了？", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還記得你是怎麼昏倒的嗎？", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我開著船，然後老耶奇跳了過來，然後......嘶......", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後船失控了，沖上了岸，把你們兩個甩了出來。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶奇大師呢？", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "耶奇大師比你先醒來，已經帶著極境先進去勘測了。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，還有船上的裝備！", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_saw_n_2", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放在船上的那些設備基本都損壞了，勘測設備......已經讓黛柯綺加緊製造了。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開鑿設備倒是不用了。", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_saw_n_2", "volume": 0.2, "delay": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼？", "name": "斯第奇·畫布"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從剛才開始，你就沒有感覺到有什麼東西很吵嗎？", "name": "阿芙朵嘉"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "阿芙朵嘉無奈地向著不遠處看了一眼。"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_saw_n_2", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall", "volume": 0.2, "delay": 0.5}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在她的提醒下，斯第奇才意識到，原來，剛才開始就存在的噪音並不是天然的。這似乎是一種電鋸轟鳴和山岩崩塌的混合聲？"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "dialog", "attri